          "question": "What if my parent's needs change and they need more meals per week?",
          "answer": "Most standard programs provide 10 meals weekly (hot plus cold, Monday-Friday). If your parent needs more, ask about additional services or look into Medicaid waiver programs that can provide up to 14 meals per week as part of a broader care plan."
